*stream_socket_get_name*

(PHP 5, PHP 7, PHP 8)

stream_socket_get_name â€” Retrieve the name of the local or remote sockets

===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  stream_socket_get_name(resource $socket, bool $remote): string|false~

Returns the local or remote name of a given socket connection.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

{socket}

  The socket to get the name of.

{remote}

  If set to true the remote socket name will be returned, if set to false the
  local socket name will be returned.

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

The name of the socket, or false on failure.

===============================================================================
